name: GKTurnBasedExchangeStatus
desc: The status of an exchange or reply.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: The state of the exchange request is unknown.

items.name: case active
items.desc: GameKit sent the exchange request to recipients but not all recipients replied.

items.name: case complete
items.desc: All recipients of the exchange request replied.

items.name: case resolved
items.desc: The current participant saved the exchange request.

items.name: case canceled
items.desc: The sender canceled the exchange request.
